-- Prudential Promotes Juliano, Hoyer to Lead Collateralized Loans
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-02-13T16:48:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-13/prudential-promotes-juliano-hoyer-to-lead-collateralized-loans.html
Prudential Financial Inc., the
second-biggest U.S. life insurer, promoted Brian Juliano and
Bent Hoyer to co-heads of the company’s U.S. collateralized loan
obligation business.  Juliano, previously a portfolio manager, and Hoyer, a vice
president, replace Sara Bonesteel, who moved into a lead role
for Prudential’s U.S. general account, the Newark, New Jersey-
based insurer said today in a statement on its web site.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elizabeth Bunn in New York at 
 ebunn1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
